10 An Act relating to investment accounts; creating the
Oklahoma Dream Accounts Investment Program Act;
11 defining terms; creating the Oklahoma Dream Account
Investment Program; authorizing one-time
12 contributions to certain Trump Accounts; requiring
verification; making contributions subject to
13 availability of funds; prescribing order of
contributions; requiring the State Treasurer to
14 prescribe form; authorizing State Treasurer to
promulgate rules; providing construing provisions;
